2017年3月22日下午約2點40分，[[英國國會|英國國會]]大樓外發生“恐怖襲擊”。一男子首先在附近的[[西敏橋|西敏橋]]上用汽车冲撞行人，造成大量伤亡，再持刀攻击国会大樓警卫。疑犯被当场击毙。事件造成6人死亡，約50人傷。

==案發經過==
在下午2時40分左右，一輛汽車在西敏橋上冲撞多達十位行人。其後，一名穿著黑色衣服的男子在Old Palace Yard用刀攻擊警察。在警方警告無效後，兩名便衣警員向他開了3至4槍。空中救護員隨後到達，嘗試為兇手進行急救。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-39355940|title=Parliament shooting: Police officer 'stabbed'|publisher=英国广播公司|date=2017-03-23|accessdate=2017-03-22|archive-date=2017-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170322152019/http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-39355940|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/blog/live/2017/mar/22/peers-say-brexit-with-no-trade-deal-would-cause-signicicant-damage-to-service-sector-politics-live|title=Parliament attack: man shot after police officer stabbed and several injured in related incident - live updates|publisher=卫报|date=2017-03-22|accessdate=2017-03-22|archive-date=2018-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180401094654/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/blog/live/2017/mar/22/peers-say-brexit-with-no-trade-deal-would-cause-signicicant-damage-to-service-sector-politics-live|dead-url=no}}</ref>案發後，大部分[[英國下議院|下議院]]議員留在會議廳避難作預防措施，其他國會工作人員也被告知要留在辦公室。這事件已被[[倫敦警察廳|倫敦警察廳]]視為恐怖襲擊，其後所有議員及工作人員到達[[西敏寺|西敏寺]]暫避。截至下午4時23分，事件已造成一名女性受害者死亡。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/uk-39355505|title=Parliament shooting -latest updates|publisher=英国广播公司|date=2017-03-22|accessdate=2017-03-22|archive-date=2018-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180404083228/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/uk-39355505|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==死傷==
事件最終共造成包括嫌犯在内的6人死亡，至少50人受伤<ref name="five dead others">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-39359158|title=London attack: Five dead in Westminster terror attack|publisher=BBC新闻|date=2017-03-22|accessdate=2017-03-23|archive-date=2018-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180327050624/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-39359158|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其中，2位分屬英國與美國籍的平民遭到車輛撞擊，一人當場死亡，另一人因重傷於醫院搶救無效死亡。而48岁的{{le|议会及外交保卫队|Parliamentary and Diplomatic Protection}}当值指挥官基斯·帕尔玛（{{lang|en|Keith Palmer}}）則因遭到歹徒持刀刺殺失血过多而去世<ref>{{cite web |url=http://metro.co.uk/2017/03/22/keith-palmer-named-as-officer-killed-in-terror-attack-as-five-confirmed-dead-6527902/ |title=Keith Palmer named as officer killed in London terror attack as five confirmed dead | Metro News |publisher=Metro.co.uk |date=2016-03-22 |accessdate=2017-03-22 |archive-date=2019-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725154254/https://metro.co.uk/2017/03/22/keith-palmer-named-as-officer-killed-in-terror-attack-as-five-confirmed-dead-6527902/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBC-39355505">{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/uk-39355505|title=London attack - latest updates|work=BBC新闻|accessdate=2017-03-22|archive-date=2018-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180404083228/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/uk-39355505|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Batchelor">{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/keith-palmer-policeman-stabbing-death-named-london-terror-attack-westminster-a7644811.html|title=Keith Palmer: Policeman stabbed to death in London terror attack named|last=Batchelor|first=Tom|date=2017-03-22|work=独立报|accessdate=2017-03-22|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113213140/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/keith-palmer-policeman-stabbing-death-named-london-terror-attack-westminster-a7644811.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外，12人伤势嚴重，其中有人伤势据称“十分危急”<ref name="Boyle">{{cite news|last1=Boyle|first1=Danny|last2=Evans|first2=Martin|title=Parliament shooting: Knifeman shot by police after charging through Westminster gates and stabbing officer|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/03/22/man-shot-police-outside-parliament-officer-reportedly-shoots|work=每日电讯报|accessdate=2017-03-22|archive-date=2017-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170323212543/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/03/22/man-shot-police-outside-parliament-officer-reportedly-shoots/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，另有八人伤势较轻，在襲擊现场得到救治。

受伤民众被分別送往横跨西敏桥的[[兰贝斯|兰贝斯]][[圣托马斯医院|圣托马斯医院]]、{{le|国王大学医院|King's College Hospital}}创伤急救中心、[[圣玛丽医院_(伦敦)|圣玛丽医院]]、[[皇家伦敦医院|皇家伦敦医院]]和{{le|車路士和西敏医院|Chelsea and Westminster Hospital}}<ref name="BBC-39355505" /><ref name="Sparrow">{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/blog/live/2017/mar/22/peers-say-brexit-with-no-trade-deal-would-cause-signicicant-damage-to-service-sector-politics-live|title=Parliament attack: man shot after police officer stabbed at House of Commons|last=Sparrow|first=Andrew|work=卫报|accessdate=2017-03-22|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2018-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180401094654/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/blog/live/2017/mar/22/peers-say-brexit-with-no-trade-deal-would-cause-signicicant-damage-to-service-sector-politics-live|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在泰晤士河中获救的罗马尼亚籍女遊客，因傷勢過重，4月6日撤除[[生命保障系统|生命保障系统]]後于医院离世，年僅31歲。她的罗马尼亚男友原计划在伦敦旅行时向她求婚，却在袭击中受伤<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-39525596|title=Westminster Bridge attack victim Andreea Cristea dies|work=BBC News|accessdate=2017-04-07|archive-date=2017-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170408032526/http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-39525596|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CristeaTelegraph">{{cite news|work=The Daily Telegraph|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/04/07/andreea-cristea-woman-fell-thames-westminster-attack-dies-hospital/|accessdate=2017-04-07|title=Andreea Cristea: woman who fell in the Thames during the Westminster attack dies in hospital|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015114/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/04/07/andreea-cristea-woman-fell-thames-westminster-attack-dies-hospital/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一群来自法国[[布列塔尼半岛|布列塔尼]][[孔卡尔诺|孔卡尔诺]]的15-16岁学生亦在伤者之列<ref name="BBC-39355505" /><ref name="lesechos.fr">{{cite news| url= https://www.lesechos.fr/monde/europe/0211902390408-attaque-devant-le-parlement-britannique-plusieurs-blesses-2074381.php| title= Attaque à Londres : des élèves français blessés, selon Bernard Cazeneuve| location= 巴黎| website= LesEcho.fr| language= fr| date= 2017-03-22| access-date= 2017-03-22| archive-date= 2017-03-24| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170324004532/https://www.lesechos.fr/monde/europe/0211902390408-attaque-devant-le-parlement-britannique-plusieurs-blesses-2074381.php| dead-url= no}}</ref>。其他伤者包括刚参加表彰仪式返回的三名警察、两名罗马尼亚公民和四名[[边山大学|边山大学]]学生<ref name="BBC-39355505" /><ref name="Sparrow" />。

