==袭击者==
[[伦敦警察厅|伦敦警察厅]]确认行凶者为52岁英国人哈立德·马苏德（{{lang|en|Khalid Masood}}）<ref name="theguardian1">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/live/2017/mar/23/westminster-attack-parliament-resumes-tributes-keith-palmer-live|title=London terror attack: Khalid Masood named by police as responsible for Westminster attack|newspaper=卫报|date=2017-03-23|accessdate=2017-03-23|archive-date=2018-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180415132041/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/live/2017/mar/23/westminster-attack-parliament-resumes-tributes-keith-palmer-live|dead-url=no}}</ref>，原名阿德里安·艾尔姆斯·阿焦（{{lang|en|Adrian Elms Ajao}}）<ref name="news.com.au">{{cite web|url=http://www.news.com.au/world/europe/london-terrorists-mum-breaks-silence-after-deadly-attack/news-story/103d67bd27a690201b80442464c044d4|title=First pictures emerge of London terrorist|accessdate=2017-03-25|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111234530/https://www.news.com.au/world/europe/london-terrorists-mum-breaks-silence-after-deadly-attack/news-story/103d67bd27a690201b80442464c044d4|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Fourth victim in Westminster attack named|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-39377883|accessdate=2017-03-24|date=2017-03-24|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112010359/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-39377883|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CNN">{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2017/03/24/europe/london-attack/index.html?adkey=bn|title=London attack: Westminster suspect identified as Adrian Russell Ajao|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2017-03-24|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112012909/http://edition.cnn.com/2017/03/24/europe/london-attack/index.html?adkey=bn|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2009年，他在狱中皈依伊斯兰教，更名为哈立德·马苏德，然而警方称他还有多个化名，比如哈立德·楚德瑞（{{lang|en|Khalid Choudry}}）<ref name="news.com.au"/><ref name="Independent">{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/khalid-masood-terrorist-westminster-london-attack-who-is-he-profile-a7646336.html|title=Khalid Masood: London attacker was known to MI5 but had no terror convictions|first=Andrew|last=Griffin|date=2017-03-23|accessdate=2017-03-23|work=独立报|archive-date=2020-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810022819/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/khalid-masood-terrorist-westminster-london-attack-who-is-he-profile-a7646336.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。马苏德生于[[肯特郡|肯特郡]]，侦查人员相信他近期住在西米德兰兹郡<ref>{{cite news|last1=Brown|first1=David|last2=Swerling|first2=Gabriella|last3=Gibbons|first3=Katie|title=Police search homes linked to criminal with a string of aliases|work=泰晤士报|page=2|issn=0140-0460|date=2017-03-23}}</ref>。据报道，马苏德曾于2005年到2009年间在[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯]]担任英语教师或导师，后来回到英国，供职于卢顿的{{le|英语外教|TEFL}}学院<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2017/mar/24/nine-custody-westminster-terrorist-attack-police-arrests|title=Westminster attack: terrorist's final hours and violent past|last=Grierson|first=Jamie|date=2017-03-24|work=卫报|access-date=2017-03-24|last2=Dodd|first2=Vikram|language=en-gb|issn=0261-3077|last3=Laville|first3=Sandra|last4=Ross|first4=Alice|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127110407/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2017/mar/24/nine-custody-westminster-terrorist-attack-police-arrests|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

此前，他曾被军情五处调查，但苏格兰场称马苏德并非当前调查的对象，之前也没有情报显示他策动恐怖袭击<ref name="Bilefsky">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/03/23/world/europe/london-attack-uk.html|title=London Attacker Identified as Khalid Masood|last=Bilefsky|first=Dan|work=纽约时报|accessdate=2017-03-23|location=伦敦|archive-date=2018-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630071144/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/03/23/world/europe/london-attack-uk.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不过，他此前多次因袭击被定罪，包括[[严重身体伤害|严重身体伤害]]、持有侵犯性武器且早在1983年破坏公共秩序，唯独未被判任何恐怖主义罪行<ref name="autogenerated1">{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-39372154|title=London attack: Police name Westminster attacker|date=2017-03-23|publisher=BBC新闻|accessdate=2017-03-23|language=en-gb|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112014244/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-39372154|dead-url=no}}</ref>。部分媒体披露马苏德接受治疗的照片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sky.com/story/joking-attacker-khalid-masood-on-whatsapp-before-westminster-murders-10812571|title=Attacker on WhatsApp before murders|accessdate=2017-03-25|archive-date=2017-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170623072431/http://news.sky.com/story/joking-attacker-khalid-masood-on-whatsapp-before-westminster-murders-10812571|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sky.com/story/westminster-attack-first-picture-of-suspect-10810877|title=Westminster attack: First picture of suspect|publisher=天空新闻台|accessdate=2017-03-22|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111162541/http://news.sky.com/story/westminster-attack-first-picture-of-suspect-10810877|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

有报道指，袭击前马苏德曾在萨塞克斯郡[[布莱顿|布莱顿]]的普雷斯顿公园酒店（{{lang|en|Preston Park Hotel}}）过夜，但经理表示报道“开玩笑”<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/live/2017/mar/24/london-attack-police-terrorist-khalid-masood-live|title=London terror attack: police name fourth fatality and make two 'significant' arrests – live|last=Khomami|first=Nadia|date=2017-03-24|work=卫报|access-date=2017-03-24|last2=Phipps|first2=Claire|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127194512/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/live/2017/mar/24/london-attack-police-terrorist-khalid-masood-live|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之前在2000年，当时那里属东萨塞克斯郡[[莱伊_(东萨塞克斯)|莱伊]]管辖，当地{{le|北亚姆|Northiam}}村的一位居民持刀袭击公屋居民被判入狱两年。2003年获释后，他又在萨塞克斯持刀伤人，又被判入狱六个月<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/03/23/violent-extremist-dropped-polices-radar/|accessdate=2017-03-24|work=每日电讯报|title=First picture of Khalid Masood reveals how he went from football-loving teenager to London attacker|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125215047/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/03/23/violent-extremist-dropped-polices-radar/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="tele2">{{cite news|work=每日电讯报|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/03/24/khalid-masood-everything-know-london-attacker/|title=Khalid Masood: Everything we know about the London attacker|author1=Robert Mendick|author2=Emily Allen|accessdate=2017-03-24|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125215055/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/03/24/khalid-masood-everything-know-london-attacker/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

官方怀疑袭击与伊斯兰极端主义有关<ref name="wls">{{cite news |url=http://abc7chicago.com/news/5-dead-in-london-attacks-including-police-officer-and-attacker-british-police-say/1812798 |title=5 dead in London attacks, including police officer and attacker, British police say |date=2017-03-22 |agency=Associated Press |publisher=WLS-TV |accessdate=2017-03-23 |location=伦敦 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170323014153/http://abc7chicago.com/news/5-dead-in-london-attacks-including-police-officer-and-attacker-british-police-say/1812798/ |archivedate=2017-03-23 }}</ref>，然而[[内政大臣_(英国)|内政大臣]][[安珀·路德|安珀·路德]]更怀疑马苏德是否隶属于[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Hamilton|first1=Fiona|last2=Ford|first2=Richard|last3=Dominic|first3=Kennedy|last4=Simpson|first4=John|title=Killer was Muslim convert|url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/edition/news/killer-was-muslim-convert-0b66607fv|accessdate=2017-03-24|work=泰晤士报|subscription=y|date=2017-03-24|archive-date=2019-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190421065347/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/edition/news/killer-was-muslim-convert-0b66607fv|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月23日，伊斯兰国非官方机构[[阿马克新闻社|阿马克新闻社]]宣传袭击者“是伊斯兰国的战士，发动行动是回应多国联军袭击平民<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/03/23/london-attack-seven-arrested-police-raid-properties-linked-islamist|title=London attack: ISIL claims responsibility as Theresa May reveals terrorist was British citizen who had been investigated by MI5|work=每日电讯报|date=2017-03-23|accessdate=2017-03-23|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111224044/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/03/23/london-attack-seven-arrested-police-raid-properties-linked-islamist/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”分析人员监测组织网站，表示该声明似乎是为了掩饰伊斯兰国在伊拉克和叙利亚的损失，并补充道，由于缺乏袭击者的生平信息和袭击事件的细节，伊斯兰国并未直接参与事件<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/isis-london-westminster-parliament-attack-claim-syria-iraq-islamic-state-militants-plan-what-does-it-a7646871.html|title=Isis claiming responsibility for London attack to mask huge losses in Iraq and Syria, say terror experts|author=Lizzie Dearden|work=独立报|accessdate=2017-03-23|archive-date=2019-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524182730/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/isis-london-westminster-parliament-attack-claim-syria-iraq-islamic-state-militants-plan-what-does-it-a7646871.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

